stories.title: Symonds seals Australian win
stories.subTitle: Sri Lanka v Australia, 3rd ODI, Colombo
stories.summary: Australia bounced back from their one-run defeat at Dambulla, and thedistraction of Adam Gilchrist and Andrew Symonds' disciplinary inquiries, to reclaim the advantage in this five-match series with a comfortable five-wicket victory against Sri Lanka
